{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9be123f8bf","title":"七绝·戏改李攀龙《怀明卿","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5b6317c72b","index":0,"year":1971,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"9be123f8bf"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji51","name":"毛泽东全集第51卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/51-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji51":{"comments":[{"id":"61428ad500","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"9be123f8bf","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"豫章，古地名，其地在准南江北之界。汉移其名于江南，置郡，属扬州。辖境相当于今江西省。隋平陈，改为县，属洪州，辖境逐渐缩小，故治所在今南昌市。故用来指江西或南昌。彩云间，唐代季白《早发白帝城》诗：“朝辞白帝彩云间。"},{"id":"15b0e762c9","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"9be123f8bf","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"九派，指江西九江市北的一段长江。这里江水有九个支流，故叫九派。九叠山，江西庐山名胜之一，又名九叠屏，这里指代庐山。九派长江九登山，李攀龙的诗意思是说远望江西方向，遥想那里有长江九派、庐山九登，表示怀念吴国伦。毛泽东这里借指江西庐山。"},{"id":"9c6c083bd7","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"9be123f8bf","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"高卧，高枕而卧，喻指隐居不仕。石镜，光亮明净，可以照人的山石。"},{"id":"2dad0d5256","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"9be123f8bf","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛泽东这里是说，林彪只宜高卧睡大觉，不须霜照石镜，因为他在庐山会议上安图集夺党和国家领导权的阴谋，已经败露。在秋风萧瑟之中，那种恼羞成怒的脸色一定是很难着的，辛辣地讽刺了林彪的数徒嘴脸。"}],"contents":[{"id":"bb6f14a0f6","type":"title","text":"七绝·戏改李攀龙”《怀明卿》","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"9be123f8bf"},{"id":"61428ad500","type":"paragraph","text":"豫章西望彩云间回","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"9be123f8bf"},{"id":"15b0e762c9","type":"paragraph","text":"九派长江九叠山","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"9be123f8bf"},{"id":"9c6c083bd7","type":"paragraph","text":"高卧不须就石镜M.","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"9be123f8bf"},{"id":"2dad0d5256","type":"paragraph","text":"秋风怒在版徒颜问","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"9be123f8bf"},{"id":"c4ae10cd9c","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]李攀龙（1514-1570），山东历城（今属济南市）人。字于鳞，号沧漠。嘉靖二十三年（1544）进士。承李梦阳、何景明等“前七子”的遗说，主张复古，与谢臻、梁有誉、宗臣、王世贞、徐中行、吴国伦，合称“后七子”，为“后七子”的领袖。著有《沧漠集》。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"9be123f8bf"}],"page":{"id":"be8c26b71d","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"9be123f8bf","start":286,"end":286}}}},"__N_SSG":true}